<!-- ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ SCRIPT ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ -->
<script>
  const exercises = [
    { id: 1,  title: 'Saludo Personalizado',      category: 'Input'      },
    { id: 2,  title: 'Contador de Clics',          category: 'Eventos'    },
    { id: 3,  title: 'Panel de Visibilidad',       category: 'Toggle'     },
    { id: 4,  title: 'Alerta de Texto',            category: 'Eventos'    },
    { id: 5,  title: 'Gestor de Tareas',           category: 'Lista'      },
    { id: 6,  title: 'Calculadora B√°sica',         category: 'C√°lculo'    },
    { id: 7,  title: 'Cambiador de Tema',          category: 'Toggle'     },
    { id: 8,  title: 'Mensaje Condicional',        category: 'Condici√≥n'  },
    { id: 9,  title: 'Nombre Completo Autom√°tico', category: 'Input'      },
    { id: 10, title: 'Detector de Cambios',        category: 'Validaci√≥n' },
  ];

  const categoryColors: Record<string, string> = {
    'Input':      '#64dcff',
    'Eventos':    '#e8ff47',
    'Toggle':     '#c084fc',
    'Lista':      '#4ade80',
    'C√°lculo':    '#ff9f47',
    'Condici√≥n':  '#fb7185',
    'Validaci√≥n': '#f97316',
  };

  const modal      = document.getElementById('modal')!;
  const modalNum   = document.getElementById('modal-number')!;
  const modalTitle = document.getElementById('modal-title')!;

  function openModal(id: number) {
    const ex = exercises.find(e => e.id === id);
    if (!ex) return;
    modalNum.textContent   = `#${String(id).padStart(2,'0')} ¬∑ ${ex.category}`;
    modalNum.style.color   = categoryColors[ex.category] ?? '#64dcff';
    modalTitle.textContent = ex.title;
    document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.ex-panel').forEach(p => p.classList.add('hidden'));
    document.querySelector<HTMLElement>(`.ex-panel[data-ex="${id}"]`)?.classList.remove('hidden');
    modal.classList.remove('hidden');
    document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
  }

  function closeModal() {
    modal.classList.add('hidden');
    document.body.style.overflow = '';
  }

  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.ex-card').forEach(card => {
    card.addEventListener('click', () => openModal(Number(card.dataset.id)));
  });
  document.getElementById('close-btn')!.addEventListener('click', closeModal);
  modal.addEventListener('click', (e) => { if (e.target === modal) closeModal(); });
  document.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
    if (!modal.classList.contains('hidden') && e.key === 'Escape') closeModal();
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 1: Saludo ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  document.getElementById('ej1-input')!.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
    const name = (e.target as HTMLInputElement).value.trim();
    document.getElementById('ej1-output')!.textContent =
      name ? `¬°Bienvenido/a, ${name}! üëã` : '¬°Hola! ¬øCu√°l es tu nombre?';
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 2: Contador ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  let count = 0;
  const ej2Count = document.getElementById('ej2-count')!;
  document.getElementById('ej2-btn')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    ej2Count.textContent = String(++count);
  });
  document.getElementById('ej2-reset')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    count = 0;
    ej2Count.textContent = '0';
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 3: Visibilidad ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  document.getElementById('ej3-btn')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    document.getElementById('ej3-msg')!.classList.toggle('hidden');
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 4: Alerta ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  document.getElementById('ej4-btn')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    const val = (document.getElementById('ej4-input') as HTMLInputElement).value;
    alert(val || '(El campo est√° vac√≠o)');
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 5: Tareas ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  const ej5Input = document.getElementById('ej5-input') as HTMLInputElement;
  const ej5List  = document.getElementById('ej5-list')!;

  function agregarTarea() {
    const texto = ej5Input.value.trim();
    if (!texto) return;
    const li = document.createElement('li');
    li.className = 'task-item';
    li.innerHTML = `<span class="task-text">${texto}</span><button class="task-del">Eliminar</button>`;
    li.querySelector('button')!.addEventListener('click', () => li.remove());
    ej5List.appendChild(li);
    ej5Input.value = '';
    ej5Input.focus();
  }
  document.getElementById('ej5-btn')!.addEventListener('click', agregarTarea);
  ej5Input.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => { if (e.key === 'Enter') agregarTarea(); });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 6: Calculadora ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  const ej6Result = document.getElementById('ej6-result')!;
  document.querySelectorAll<HTMLElement>('.calc-op').forEach(btn => {
    btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
      const a = parseFloat((document.getElementById('ej6-a') as HTMLInputElement).value);
      const b = parseFloat((document.getElementById('ej6-b') as HTMLInputElement).value);
      if (isNaN(a) || isNaN(b)) { ej6Result.textContent = 'Ingresa dos n√∫meros v√°lidos.'; return; }
      const op = (btn as HTMLElement).dataset.op;
      let result = '';
      if (op === 'sum') result = `${a} + ${b} = ${a + b}`;
      else if (op === 'sub') result = `${a} ‚àí ${b} = ${a - b}`;
      else if (op === 'mul') result = `${a} √ó ${b} = ${a * b}`;
      else if (op === 'div') {
        if (b === 0) { ej6Result.textContent = '‚ö†Ô∏è Error: divisi√≥n entre cero.'; return; }
        result = `${a} √∑ ${b} = ${+(a / b).toFixed(6)}`;
      }
      ej6Result.textContent = 'Resultado: ' + result;
    });
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 7: Tema ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  let isDark = true;
  const ej7Btn   = document.getElementById('ej7-btn')!;
  const ej7Inner = document.getElementById('ej7-inner')!;
  ej7Btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
    isDark = !isDark;
    ej7Inner.className = `theme-preview ${isDark ? 'dark-mode' : 'light-mode'}`;
    ej7Btn.textContent = isDark ? 'üåô Activar Modo Claro' : '‚òÄÔ∏è Activar Modo Oscuro';
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 8: Condicional ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  const ej8Output = document.getElementById('ej8-output')!;
  document.getElementById('ej8-a')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    ej8Output.textContent = 'üìò Este es el mensaje A';
  });
  document.getElementById('ej8-b')!.addEventListener('click', () => {
    ej8Output.textContent = 'üìï Este es el mensaje B';
  });

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 9: Nombre completo ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  const ej9Nombre   = document.getElementById('ej9-nombre')   as HTMLInputElement;
  const ej9Apellido = document.getElementById('ej9-apellido') as HTMLInputElement;
  const ej9Output   = document.getElementById('ej9-output')!;
  function actualizarNombre() {
    const n = ej9Nombre.value.trim();
    const a = ej9Apellido.value.trim();
    ej9Output.textContent = (n || a) ? `${n} ${a}`.trim() : 'Tu nombre completo aparecer√° aqu√≠';
  }
  ej9Nombre.addEventListener('input', actualizarNombre);
  ej9Apellido.addEventListener('input', actualizarNombre);

  // ‚îÄ‚îÄ 10: Detector ‚îÄ‚îÄ
  const ej10Input   = document.getElementById('ej10-input')   as HTMLInputElement;
  const ej10Counter = document.getElementById('ej10-counter')!;
  const ej10Warn    = document.getElementById('ej10-warn')!;
  ej10Input.addEventListener('input', () => {
    const len = ej10Input.value.length;
    ej10Counter.textContent = `${len} / 10 caracteres`;
    if (len > 10) {
      ej10Warn.classList.remove('hidden');
      ej10Counter.style.color = '#f97316';
    } else {
      ej10Warn.classList.add('hidden');
      ej10Counter.style.color = 'var(--muted)';
    }
  });
</script>